      <guid>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6/14.%E5%8F%98%E9%99%90%E7%A7%AF%E5%88%86/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[高等数学] 14.变限积分</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="变限积分">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%8f%98%e9%99%90%e7%a7%af%e5%88%86"></a>
变限积分
</h2><p>原理:
</p>
$$
\int_{a}^{x} f(t) \, dt = F(x) - F(a)
$$<p>
基本形式:
</p>
$$
\left[ \int_{a}^{x} f(t) \, dt \right]' = f(x)
$$<p>
复杂形式:
</p>
$$
\left[ \int_{a}^{\varphi(x)} f(t) \, dt \right]' = f\big[\varphi(x)\big] \cdot \big[\varphi(x)\big]'
$$<p>
一般形式:
</p>
$$
\left[ \int_{\varphi_{1}(x)}^{\varphi_{2}(x)} f(t) \, dt \right]' = f\big[\varphi_{2}(x)\big] \cdot \big[\varphi_{2}(x)\big]' - f\big[\varphi_{1}(x)\big] \cdot \big[\varphi_{1}(x)\big]'
$$<blockquote>
<p><img src="/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6/14.%E5%8F%98%E9%99%90%E7%A7%AF%E5%88%86/image-20260703204200085.png" alt="image-20260703204200085"></p>
        
