      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[高等数学] 11.渐近线</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="渐近线">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e6%b8%90%e8%bf%91%e7%ba%bf"></a>
渐近线
</h2><ul>
<li><strong>铅直渐近线/垂直渐近线</strong>: 无穷间断点</li>
<li><strong>水平渐近线</strong>: $\displaystyle\lim_{x \to +\infty}f(x)$ 和 $\displaystyle\lim_{x \to -\infty}f(x)$</li>
<li><strong>斜渐近线</strong>
(当求出两条水平渐近线的时候, 可以直接说函数没有斜渐近线)
<ul>
<li>$\displaystyle\lim_{x \to +\infty} \frac{f(x)}{x} = a \ (a\text{为非零常数}),\quad \lim_{x \to +\infty} \big[f(x)-ax\big] = b \ (b\text{为常数}) \implies y=ax+b \text{ 是斜渐近线}$</li>
<li>$\displaystyle\lim_{x \to -\infty} \frac{f(x)}{x} = a \ (a\text{为非零常数}),\quad \lim_{x \to -\infty} \big[f(x)-ax\big] = b \ (b\text{为常数}) \implies y=ax+b \text{ 是斜渐近线}$</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p><img src="/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6/11.%E6%B8%90%E8%BF%91%E7%BA%BF/image-20260703131059901.png" alt="image-20260703131059901"></p>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-07-03首发于<a href='https://byzhrichard.github.io/'>byzh的博客</a>，最后修改于2026-07-03</p>]]>
